唔自私應該是他們親口講先有判定"},{"pid":"1fe8e2969426151c4d0b9cf6d3b4ffa520e6fa38","tid":753613,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T21:59:49.000Z","msg":"分別咪就係有生同無生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1a53db44699d7f50f83c829abe24d9f122f465","tid":753613,"uid":10208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T22:01:15.000Z","msg":"分別係子女受苦同唔洗受苦"},{"pid":"a7b3932a38864481d98a4aaf0d373874eb4a6031","tid":753613,"uid":160146,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8bb77899857b6604d69c1c83c0449644c0a14d06","tid":753613,"uid":74918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31652f71f36e7a86da58446005bf2c37a3c37582","tid":753613,"uid":160146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5480a881a31a8076c6c4e6bdbd8e946e1b1f9778","tid":753613,"uid":74918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:16:49.000Z","msg":"咁呢個好似只係你既價值觀<br />\n你用你自己既價值觀去定義人地既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:34:09.000Z","msg":"我只係想討論，並不係想定義人地<br />\n正如連登仔會挑戰廢老養兒防老的價值觀<br />\n我亦都覺得窮人唔好生仔並非絕對錯誤，但是如果將佢視為金科玉律，只會助長跨代貧窮，就算有可能改變下一代命運都因為太早卻步而唔成事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T20:54:39.000Z","msg":"咁視乎你睇仔女係一個人定係一個工具去看待<br />\n窮人好容易將仔女當工具<br />\n例如生多個係想要間大D既公屋<br />\n或者多D綜援<br />\n所以係安全網下生多幾個係好架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T22:07:44.000Z","msg":"當然，如果將仔女當成工具，就算係有錢家庭都唔會開心。所以真正問題唔應該係窮人生唔生仔，而係如果要生仔，窮人應該要有咩心態"},{"pid":"b1eda6bb4098445b1dcf3951a2bd43a6783e7677","tid":753613,"uid":80053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:20:47.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"37a64af50eebc9427e8021f8d35e4daf0539a00a","tid":753613,"uid":132461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fde4abdd905640fa2b0ca757008f6f17785b9db","tid":753613,"uid":160146,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"668ec733cad2e9cef516b65ab57c5825f47e9b3d","tid":753613,"uid":74918,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"49673123df41c8c8dc34d99070e0415ab